-- Ex-divs to take up to 3.64 points off FTSE 100 on March 26
-- 
-- Mon Mar 24, 2014 06:28AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, March 24 (Reuters) - The following FTSE 100 <.FTSE> companies will go ex-dividend on Wednesday, after which investors will no longer qualify for the latest dividend payout.

